  description="DigiHoof terms of service for the hoof radiograph reporting platform."
>

<section class="split-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>

    <p class="operator-notice">Effective date: June 15, 2026. DigiHoof is operated by DigiScan LLC, a company organized under the laws of the United States.</p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>
      By accessing or using DigiHoof, you agree to these Terms of Service and any policies
      referenced here. If you use DigiHoof on behalf of a clinic, practice, company, or other
