      Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the platform.
    </p>

    <h2>2. The DigiHoof Service</h2>
    <p>
      DigiHoof provides cloud-based hoof radiograph reporting, measurement, workflow,
      collaboration, and sharing tools for veterinary and farrier use. DigiHoof may include
      automated image processing, artificial intelligence, measurement assistance, report
      generation, mobile sharing, and related support services.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Professional Responsibility</h2>
    <p>
      DigiHoof is a professional workflow and reporting tool. It is not a substitute for
